<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0057-en-b22c2f94" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>老子</title><editor role="translator">Tang Zhangping 湯漳平 and 王朝華</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>老子</title>北京：中華書局，2014</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0057"><title xml:lang="och">老子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="en">English</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-05-18T01:22:04.097+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0057-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:40.607+09:00">道可知而可行，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:44.964+09:00">但非恒久不变之道；</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:54.12+09:00">名可以据实而定，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:22:58.514+09:00">但非恒久不 变之名。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:23:07.642+09:00">无名.是万物的原始；</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:23:12.272+09:00">有名.是万物的开端。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:19.528+09:00">所以，经常保持清将无欲，可以体察其中的奥妙;</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:28.444+09:00">经常保持有欲追求.可以知晓道的功用。</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:42.067+09:00">这两者，同一出处而名称不同.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:49.652+09:00">都十分深远玄妙，</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:54.241+09:00">玄妙而又玄妙啊.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T01:24:55.208+09:00">这是 解开所有奥妙的门径。</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>